2K Games is a video game publishing subsidiary of Take - Two Interactive . It was created on January 25 , 2005 after Take - Two acquired developer Visual Concepts and its wholly owned subsidiary Kush Games from Sega for US$24 million . The name " 2K Games " comes from Visual Concepts ' sports game lineup typically referred to as the 2K series . 2K Games is headquartered in Manhattan . The label publishes a wide variety of console and PC titles developed both internally and externally . Family Guy Video Game ! . Sid Meier 's Pirates ! . Sid Meier 's Railroads ! . 